    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies Kemeleon encoding algorithms for encoding ML-
   KEM encapsulation keys and ciphertexts as random bytestrings.
   Kemeleon encodings provide obfuscation of encapsulation keys and
   ciphertexts, relying on module LWE assumptions.</t>
